OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRoyal Marines to fight MoD 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin asbestos court claim    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A group of 260 Royal Marines have      
OL,6, issued proceedings against the Ministry
OL,7, of Defence (MoD) amid claims they were 
OL,8, "knowingly" exposed to asbestos.       
OL,10,FThe potential exposure is said to have 
OL,11,Ftaken place in Latvia in 2018 and 2019 
OL,12,Fover two exercises, with a sample from 
OL,13,Fthe site allegedly containing asbestos.
OL,15,FIt is claimed the MoD breached the     
OL,16,FHuman Rights Act by "knowingly"        
OL,17,Fexposing them to the substance.        
OL,19,FThe MoD said it took troops' health and
OL,20,Fsafety "extremely seriously".          
